<collectingCountry box="[663,761,721,745]" name="Vietnam" pageId="1" pageNumber="58">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
, all other twenty-four known species are endemic to 
<collectingCountry box="[1362,1433,721,745]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="58">China</collectingCountry>
. This genus is recorded for the first time from Yunnan Province. The key is adapted from 
<bibRefCitation author="Chen" box="[1145,1433,757,781]" pageId="1" pageNumber="58" refString="Chen, S. C. &amp; He, Y. H. (2008) Phasmatodea of China. China Forestry Publishing House, Beijing, 476 pp." type="book" year="2008">
Chen and He (
<number box="[1306,1367,757,781]" pageId="1" pageNumber="58" value="2008.0">2008</number>
: 
<number box="[1378,1424,757,781]" pageId="1" pageNumber="58" value="132.0">132</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
